    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "PG Buffer Cache Hit Ratio",
      "description": "Server-wide shared-buffer hit percentage; sustained values below 90% mean disk-bound reads. Populates after the next deploy ships the extra postgres_exporter collectors (stat_database/locks/database in infra/alloy/config.alloy).",
